  "text": "The purpose of Issue 3 is to demonstrate the comparison of psychometric properties between the AX-CPT as administered in a laboratory setting and on the MTurk platform. To our knowledge, there is only one published study using the AX-CPT on MTurk, and this study used Dot Pattern Expectancy task. Like [CITATION_1] , this study of the Dot Pattern Expectancy task did not report any psychometric measures or direct comparisons with a laboratory version [CITATION_2] .",
